<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV29">
<l>iṉṉaṉṉa tūtemmai yāḷaṟṟap paṭṭiran tāḷivaḷeṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṉṉaṉṉa collā peṭaiyoṭum pōyvarum nīlamuṇṭa</l>
<l>miṉṉaṉṉa mēṉip perumā ṉulakiṟpeṇ tūtucellā</l>
<l>vaṉṉaṉṉa nīrmaiko lōkuṭic cīrmaiyi laṉṉaṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“She, suffering ruin on account of a man, begs us [to bear] such message”,</l>
<l>without speaking thus, along with [their] females [they] will go [and] come.</l>
<l>Not going as a woman’s messengers into the world of the great lord with a lightning-like body that has absorbed blue,</l>
<l>is thus [your] nature, oh geese without excellence of family?</l>
<l></l>
<l>b (traditional)</l>
<l>suffering from the absence of a man (whom she could send)</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
